        <briefdescription>
<para>Estimated current memory usage of the program, in bytes. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Fetched from system using VK_EXT_memory_budget extension if enabled.</para>
<para>It might be different than `statistics.blockBytes` (usually higher) due to additional implicit objects also occupying the memory, like swapchain, pipelines, descriptor heaps, command buffers, or `VkDeviceMemory` blocks allocated outside of this library, if any. </para>
